        public PlayerWarningExpired(Player player,
                            CommandSource source,
                            String reason)
        The event fired when a warning expires. This can be either a automatic expiration based on a time constraint, or it being deleted by another CommandSource.
        Parameters:
        player - The target player being warned
        reason - The reason of the warning
        source - The CommandSource executing the warning
